dataIdInfo.idAbs: This polygon shapefile represents the sub-regional boundaries of Uganda for 2006. These are the level 2 administrative boundaries (ADM2). The sub-regions are a level intermediate between the regions and the districts, but they are not a partition of the country; there are no sub-regions in Central, and a few districts elsewhere don't fall under any sub-region.
